      <div class="border-l-4 border-red-500 pl-4">
        <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Pre-existing Conditions</h4>
        <p class="text-neutral-600">ACA plans cannot deny coverage or charge more for pre-existing conditions—this is a major advantage. International plans often exclude pre-existing conditions initially. For those with health conditions, ACA is typically the best option once Green Card is issued.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

