        <p class="text-amber-700 font-medium">Source of funds documentation extremely challenging—had to trace 25 years of property transactions, mortgages, and sales. Multiple RFEs from USCIS. Attorney fees escalated to $45,000. Eventually approved after 38 months. Now in US with Green Card. Lesson: Complex wealth sources significantly complicate EB-5.</p>
